SciMed Life Systems Inc &lt;SMLS> saidBristol-Myers Co is analyzing the pending lawsuit broughtagainst SciMed by &lt;Advanced Cardiovascular Systems Inc> todetermine whether to consummate its previously announced plansto merge with SciMed.    The company said its was served the suit in Minneapolis onMarch 31, the day after it announced its definitive mergeragreement with Bristol-Myers.    SciMed said the suit, which alleges that SciMed infringedon Advanced Cardiovascular patents, is without merit. Reuter&#3;